file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: LTG300 algorithm
  description: LTG300 algorithm
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: 'https://algo.timetable.cheburerker.ml'
tags:
  - name: "algorithm"
  - name: "assessment"
paths:
  /algorithm/timetable/?assessment={assessment}:
    parameters:
      - name: assessment
        in: path
        example: true
    post:
      tags:
        - "algorithm"
      summary: "Generate new timetable"
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                students:
                  type: array
                  items:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/student'
                teachers:
                  type: array
                  items:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/teacher'
                auditoriums:
                  type: array
                  items:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/auditorium'
                quantities:
                  type: array
                  items:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/quantity'
                determinantType:
                  type: string
                  example: "greedy"
                  description: edge cost fuction. Only 'greedy' available.
                dataHandlers:
                  type: array
                  items:
                    type: string
                  example: [ "gcd_compressor" ]
                  description: "Input data optimizers. Only 'gcd_compressor' available."
      responses:
        "200":
          description: "OK"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  timetable:
                    $ref: "#/components/schemas/timetable"
                  assessment:
                    $ref: "#/components/schemas/assessment"
        "400":
          description: "Something wrong with input"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  status:
                    type: "string"
                    example: "error"
                  description:
                    type: string
                    example: "Serialization error"
components:
  schemas:
    auditorium:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          example: 1
          required: true
        possibleSubjects:
          type: array
          required: true
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/subject"
          example: [ { "id": 0 }, { "id": 1 }, { "id": 2 }, { "id": 3 } ]
    subject:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          example: 0
    timerange:
      type: object
      properties:
        begin:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          example: 2
          required: true
        end:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          example: 7
          required: true
    student:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          example: 1
          required: true
        timeRanges:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/timerange"
    teacher:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          example: 1
          required: true
        maxInRow:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          example: 3
          required: true
        timeRanges:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/timerange"
    quantity:
      type: object
      properties:
        lesson:
          type: object
          properties:
            studentId:
              type: integer
              format: int64
              example: 1
            teacherId:
              type: integer
              format: int64
              example: 2
            subject:
              type: integer
              example: 0
            duration:
              type: integer
              format: int64
              example: 2
        frequency:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          example: 3
          description: double lesson three times at week
    lesson:
      type: object
      properties:
        student:
          type: integer
        teacher:
          type: integer
        auditorium:
          type: integer
        subject:
          type: integer
        time:
          type: integer
        duration:
          type: integer
    timetable:
      type: object
      properties:
        lessons:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/lesson"
    assessment:
      type: object
      properties:
        isGood:
          type: boolean
          example: false
        undoneQuantities:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/quantity"
